{
  "title": "Cozy French Strong Wholemeal Flour Quiche",
  "description": "A peppery, bouncy, and cozy French dish featuring strong wholemeal flour, mirepoix-base, and plant-based-friendly ingredients. Perfect for a breakfast or brunch gathering.",
  "cuisine": "french",
