  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Roll out the dough to a thickness of 1/8 inch (3 mm).",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the flour, water, plant-based milk, pepper, nutritional yeast, and salt.",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and chopped spinach to the bowl and mix until well combined.",
    "Pour the mixture into the dough-lined tart pan and spread evenly.",
    "Drizzle the olive oil over the top and sprinkle with turmeric.",
    "Bake for 35-40 minutes or until the crust is golden brown and the filling is set.",
    "Let the quiche cool for 10-15 minutes before serving."
  ],
